{"tid":947511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多流星碎石都打唔中地球?","createTime":"2018-12-19T10:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T14:03:16.000Z","uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"016eadd90ace1a3700b51d120b2e63a4d3e6668c","tid":947511,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"地球歷史，在地球由原始太陽星雲的部份物質構成後計起，科學家估計大約有46億到50億年之間。而因為表述這麼長久的時間有所困難，可將地球的歷史模擬為二十四小時（將地球形成的時間設定為凌晨零時，而此時此刻為翌日的凌晨零時），每秒大約代表5萬3000年，而大爆炸與宇宙形成的時刻，則大約在137億年前[1]，以此模擬時間來說約等於三日前，即地球誕生前兩日。<br />\n<br />\n咁多億年都打唔中? 地球真係福地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da87b0cd8226756c382d3df47a0a830427d064e1","tid":947511,"uid":77092,"like":10,"dislike":14,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4ec0a5faf54c9d48ce214ea9fd250da1c7522dc","tid":947511,"uid":223790,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6bdfe6e8bdf5806c75ee8ca51dfd4ae33612712","tid":947511,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"好似係因為有木星幫拖"},{"pid":"9506c39a20ea82ba3937947d244f867bee976d3c","tid":947511,"uid":23295,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:21:52.000Z","msg":"侏羅紀果次唔計？"},{"pid":"233f9f8465f7aeb87be6acc0a6fa50393057e0d9","tid":947511,"uid":18251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"月球幫手擋咗唔小。"},{"pid":"acd49e4c2c985e238f5d297d80d5402f1e3af4dc","tid":947511,"uid":28624,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯境內咪有遠古時期既隕石坑"},{"pid":"698f58515856ea208c511821e5e8bc3b694439cc","tid":947511,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"點解冇粒打穿南北? 或地球一分為二"},{"pid":"e1a6defa6b8ff9c390c25bb28b0b48aa40c747dc","tid":947511,"uid":2843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":